These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
Music-Genre: reggae, rock
Birthday: march, july
1. Birthday:march is in an even position##4
2. Birthday:july == Music-Genre:rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Music-Genre   | rock | reggae |
| Birthday     | july    | march   |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
City: berlin, paris
Game: domino, monopoly
1. Game:domino is in an odd position##4
2. City:paris is on the left of City:berlin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| City   | paris | berlin        |
| Game      | domino  | monopoly |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
Birthday: march, june
Flower: aconite, orchid
1. Flower:aconite is in an odd position##4
2. Birthday:june is on the left of Birthday:march##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Birthday   | june    | march |
| Flower   | aconite | orchid |

